OL,3,CWhy it's time to talk about birth
OL,4,Ctrauma and loss
OL,6,FLouise's daughter Isla was born with a
OL,7,Frare heart disease and died at just
OL,8,Fsix weeks old.
OL,10,FGrace's first daughter Violet passed
OL,11,Faway during labour after contracting
OL,12,Fsepsis, and Rebecca suffered a very
OL,13,Ftraumatic birth with her son, Charlie.
OL,15,FThe film was created in collaboration
OL,16,Fwith the ForMed Films CIC and the
OL,17,FLancashire and South Cumbria
OL,18,FReproductive Trauma Service.
