OL,3,CWhy it's time to talk about birth
OL,4,Ctrauma and loss
OL,6,FGrace decided to tell her own story of
OL,7,Floss because she knew there are other
OL,8,Fparents in the world going through the
OL,9,Fsame thing.
OL,11,F"If you have a voice, use it," Grace
OL,12,Fsaid. "The movie that we made showed
OL,13,Four real-life, everyday experiences of
OL,14,Fwhat we have to go through.
OL,16,F"When Violet passed away we had to
OL,17,Fdrive home with an empty car seat
OL,18,Fafter spending five days with her and
OL,19,Fthat's shown in the film.
