OL,3,CWhy it's time to talk about birth
OL,4,Ctrauma and loss
OL,6,F"I sat there and thought there can't
OL,7,Fjust be me. I can't be the only person
OL,8,Fin the world going through this."
OL,10,FEchoing Grace, Becky said: "My goal
OL,11,Fwas to be open about it (birth trauma)
OL,12,Fto help others.
OL,14,F"A lot of people have got in touch
OL,15,Fabout it and say 'I don't feel as
OL,16,Falone'."
