OL,3,CWhy it's time to talk about birth
OL,4,Ctrauma and loss
OL,6,FThe hope the film will empower others
OL,7,Fto open up about their own experiences
OL,8,Fno matter who they are - mother,
OL,9,Ffather, family member or friend.
OL,11,F"It is OK to talk about difficult
OL,12,Fthings," Louise said.
OL,14,F"I want people to know that if you get
OL,15,Fthe right support and use your voice -
OL,16,Fyou can come out the other end. Life
OL,17,Fis different but you can get through
OL,18,Fit."
